subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Case Keenum threw for 366 yards and 3 touchdowns, and Bryce Beall caught the go-ahead 6-yard touchdown pass off a batted ball Saturday as visiting Houston stunned No. 5 Oklahoma State, 45-35.
